		"Name": "Cutlass VTOL",
		"Details": "A 30 ton VTOL developed in the old fashion Pod and boom rotarcraft style, the Cutlass is almost exclusively fielded by Pirate warbands but sees some deployment in the Periphery as well.  Armarment is a single Howitzer 4 weapon system with an attached Periphery TAG system. Two tons of ammunition barely keep the Howie/4 fed in combat.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar or Martian biomes due to using an ICE.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 9/14 hexes / 270/420 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        50     15\n<b>Left</b>          25     15\n<b>Right</b>        25     15\n<b>Rear</b>         25     15\n\n<b>Total</b>      140     75</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Missile Jammer</color>",
